input_script:
- name: Debug information
  ansible.builtin.debug:
    msg:
      - CIS CRN ...................... {{ cis_crn }}
output_script:
- name: get cluster subdomain
  community.kubernetes.k8s_info:
    api_version: config.openshift.io/v1
    kind: Ingress
    name: cluster
  register: _cluster_subdomain
output_body:
community.kubernetes.k8s_info:
    api_version: config.openshift.io/v1
    kind: Ingress
    name: cluster
  register: _cluster_subdomain

input_script:
- name: Check my ssh-key
  community.digitalocean.digital_ocean:
    state: present
    command: ssh
    name: Debian Machine
    ssh_pub_key: "{{pub_key}}"
    api_token: "{{token}}"
output_script:
- name: add host
  community.digitalocean.digital_ocean:
    state: present
    ssh_key_ids: "{{ pub_key_id }}"
    command: droplet
    name: mydroplet
    api_token: "{{token}}"
    size_id: 512mb
    id: "{{id}}"
    region_id: ams2
    image_id: ubuntu-14-04-x64
    wait_timeout: 500
  register: my_droplet
output_body:
community.digitalocean.digital_ocean:
    state: present
    ssh_key_ids: "{{ pub_key_id }}"
    command: droplet
    name: mydroplet
    api_token: "{{token}}"
    size_id: 512mb
    id: "{{id}}"
    region_id: ams2
    image_id: ubuntu-14-04-x64
    wait_timeout: 500
  register: my_droplet
